# Installation

## From PyPI

```bash
pip install {{ pypi_name }}
```

## From Docker

```bash
docker pull {{ docker_registry }}/{{ project_name }}:latest
```

## From source

```bash
git clone https://github.com/{{ github_org }}/{{ project_name }}
cd {{ project_name }}
uv sync --all-extras --all-groups
```

